Third-party notices for Moongate
================================

Moongate.Ultima
---------------

The Moongate.Ultima project is a Linux-first port of the "Ultima" library from
UOFiddler (https://github.com/polserver/UOFiddler), itself based on the Ultima
SDK by Krrios. The original source code is released under the Beerware license:

    "THE BEER-WARE LICENSE"
    As long as you retain this notice you can do whatever you want with
    this stuff. If we meet some day, and you think this stuff is worth it,
    you can buy me a beer in return.

Modifications in this port include: replacement of System.Drawing with
SkiaSharp, removal of Windows-only client memory access (P/Invoke) and
registry-based client discovery, and namespace changes.
